2
00:01:38.220 --> 00:01:45.900
<b>Lion</b>

3
00:01:49.360 --> 00:01:51.280
Bege!

4
00:02:05.370 --> 00:02:08.820
Oh, no! Brother Oven is furious!

5
00:02:08.820 --> 00:02:10.920
Get to the port!

6
00:02:10.920 --> 00:02:13.170
There's nowhere to run on the sea!

7
00:02:13.170 --> 00:02:14.630
Nor on the land!

8
00:02:14.630 --> 00:02:17.100
Get off the ship!

9
00:02:18.350 --> 00:02:22.140
So you chose to fight, Bege!

10
00:02:22.140 --> 00:02:25.900
All right. I'll execute you now!

11
00:02:25.900 --> 00:02:29.190
This is bad, Big Sis!
We can't set sail!

12
00:02:29.190 --> 00:02:31.110
What should we do with the cake?!

13
00:02:33.990 --> 00:02:36.110
Increase our speed!

14
00:02:36.110 --> 00:02:39.240
Go straight to the port!

15
00:02:44.580 --> 00:02:47.290
Bege's ship sped up!

16
00:02:47.290 --> 00:02:51.130
What is he thinking?!
He's gonna crash into the port!

17
00:02:53.760 --> 00:02:56.010
Why isn't he slowing down?!

18
00:02:57.980 --> 00:03:00.470
Don't tell me... it's a suicide attack?!

19
00:03:06.240 --> 00:03:09.310
It's sailing onto the coast!

20
00:03:09.310 --> 00:03:10.440
Bege!

21
00:03:10.440 --> 00:03:12.910
Don't hold back! Get ready to shoot!

22
00:03:12.910 --> 00:03:15.070
You traitor!

23
00:03:16.890 --> 00:03:19.090
How about this, you little punks?

24
00:03:22.090 --> 00:03:25.590
This ship, the Nostra Castello...

25
00:03:25.590 --> 00:03:28.890
can sail on both water and land!

26
00:03:47.070 --> 00:03:48.590
Bege!

27
00:03:49.620 --> 00:03:52.400
The paddles turned into tank caterpillars!

28
00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:55.330
I didn't think that was even possible!

29
00:03:55.330 --> 00:03:58.390
That's because I never told you!

30
00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:07.180
Why would I show all my tricks to the people
I had already decided to betray?!

31
00:04:07.180 --> 00:04:08.890
You scumbag!

32
00:04:08.890 --> 00:04:11.150
Shoot-rero !

33
00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:15.410
Chiffon! Hand the cake over to us!

34
00:04:15.410 --> 00:04:16.540
What?!

35
00:04:16.540 --> 00:04:18.960
That's impossible! The cake is gigantic!

36
00:04:18.960 --> 00:04:22.880
How are we going to hand such a big cake
over to a ship moving that fast?!

37
00:04:34.140 --> 00:04:36.850
What?! Whaaat?!

38
00:04:36.850 --> 00:04:41.580
The carriage is in the air?!

39
00:04:46.270 --> 00:04:47.950
What's happening?!

40
00:04:50.860 --> 00:04:53.200
What?!

41
00:04:54.760 --> 00:04:56.330
Black Leg!

42
00:04:57.760 --> 00:05:00.250
Make room on the deck, Bege!

43
00:05:01.640 --> 00:05:03.670
Sanji-san !

44
00:05:08.310 --> 00:05:10.430
Madam Pudding!

45
00:05:18.600 --> 00:05:20.660
Hurry up, Bege!

46
00:05:20.680 --> 00:05:22.720
Step back, guys!

47
00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:24.510
Make room on the deck!

48
00:05:24.510 --> 00:05:28.130
Y-Yes, Father!

49
00:05:28.130 --> 00:05:31.630
Black Leg... All right, come aboard!

50
00:05:34.710 --> 00:05:36.260
Who the hell is that?!

51
00:05:36.260 --> 00:05:38.640
He's using just one leg...

52
00:05:38.640 --> 00:05:40.640
Is he a cook?!

53
00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:44.980
Okay! Let's go!

54
00:05:44.980 --> 00:05:48.760
Everyone! Brace for impact!

55
00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:15.820
The cake made it aboard!

56
00:06:17.140 --> 00:06:20.820
That was amazing, Black Leg!

57
00:06:20.820 --> 00:06:23.000
What is this wonderful fragrance?

58
00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:25.410
A-As expected of Germa!

59
00:06:25.410 --> 00:06:26.960
I'm not a member of Germa!

60
00:06:26.960 --> 00:06:29.900
Bege! Pez!

61
00:06:29.900 --> 00:06:32.160
Are you alright, honey?

62
00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:34.290
Yes...

63
00:06:36.500 --> 00:06:39.630
You've always been so reckless...

64
00:06:42.290 --> 00:06:44.550
Thank you!

65
00:06:47.260 --> 00:06:50.330
Madam Pudding! Stay with us!

66
00:06:58.430 --> 00:07:00.230
I'm not gonna let them get away!

67
00:07:00.230 --> 00:07:01.390
Watch out!

68
00:07:01.390 --> 00:07:04.860
Minister Oven!
Please get out of the way!

69
00:07:04.860 --> 00:07:08.130
Don't you know who I am?!

70
00:07:08.130 --> 00:07:10.330
I'll stop them!

71
00:07:12.120 --> 00:07:12.160
SQUISH!

72
00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:12.210
SQUISH!

73
